description.content:
If you looking for a Wordpress expert and you need an Online Store to smoothly run your business, then you are Welcome to my Gig.

I am working from last 8+ Years in web development, installation, designing, and configuration of Wordpress with online store. My mostly work on ecommerce website development and completed multiple ecommerce store website for different companies. Few sample work can be visited on my portfolio

https://sarahalee.com

My Services are

  • Hosting/ domain configuration
  • Wordpress Installation
  • woocommerce configuration
  • Responsive and Professional ecommerce website design 
  • Theme and plugin installation
  • Adding Products and Categories
  • Social Media Integration
  • Google Map Integration
  • SSL Configuration for security
  • Multiple Currency
  • Mobile Friendly 
  • Payment Gateway Integration
  • Setup for Shipping
  • Slider Setting
  • Coupon System and Wishlist
  • Login / Registration Page
  • Setting up Pages
  • Contact Us & About Us page
  • Blog

 Thanks for your Time to My Gig

Note: Please feel free to discuss project requirements and quotation before purchasing my gig.

If you hit the red icon [favorite] I will be very happy .

reviews.comment: Absolutely worth every dollar. She delivered a website that launched my business that can grow with me. She also recommended several cost effective tools that my website uses.

Saralee was fast to provide services.  Several issues had to be corrected afterward. She was able to make the corrections, but couldn't help in some areas.  The template that was used cannot be updated by me since she is the one with the license, but she assured me that it wouldn't be a problem.  She is very kind and nice to work with.

Sarah is highly rated by so many customers on Fiverr. There are many reasons why, but in summary I doubt that you will find better value for money, proactiveness, helpfulness, professionalism or quality anywhere else.
